00:19:14.156 --> 00:19:17.836
It is reported that in CRD patients, the

312
00:19:17.956 --> 00:19:21.876
prevalence of CVD ranges from 30% to

313
00:19:22.156 --> 00:19:22.726
70%,

314
00:19:23.676 --> 00:19:27.556
or in CVD patients, the progression ranges

315
00:19:27.616 --> 00:19:30.636
