00:20:08.016 --> 00:20:11.196
modifiable factors may affecting this

327
00:20:11.936 --> 00:20:12.936
disease progression.

328
00:20:14.036 --> 00:20:17.256
So this study aimed to evaluate the

329
00:20:17.296 --> 00:20:21.096
