1131
01:07:55.040 --> 01:07:58.210
there. And then we also conducted subgroup

1132
01:07:58.270 --> 01:08:00.480
analyses by age and

1133
01:08:00.590 --> 01:08:04.370
sex. So here's

1134
01:08:04.570 --> 01:08:07.330
briefly our study population characteristics.

1135
01:08:07.470 --> 01:08:11.150
We had approximately equal proportion of patients with colon and

1136
01:08:11.230 --> 01:08:14.570
