1169
01:10:14.610 --> 01:10:18.310
Then if you focus on the leftmost panel for overall survival,

1170
01:10:18.830 --> 01:10:22.810
you can see that patients that were younger or under

1171
01:10:23.010 --> 01:10:26.790
65 years of age had generally a better survival than those

1172
01:10:26.810 --> 01:10:28.890
