1185
01:11:06.750 --> 01:11:09.310
men that were over 65 years of age.

1186
01:11:11.409 --> 01:11:11.670
So

1187
01:11:12.510 --> 01:11:14.910
our study has several strengths and limitations.

1188
01:11:14.990 --> 01:11:18.310
This project was done in a very large cohort of

1189
01:11:18.750 --> 01:11:19.250
diverse

1190
01:11:20.130 --> 01:11:23.890
patients from all over the United States and international patients as well.

1191
01:11:24.080 --> 01:11:27.890
We had a multi-center design with a comprehensive long-term

1192
01:11:28.050 --> 01:11:28.460
follow-up.

1193
01:11:30.250 --> 01:11:33.590
The one big advantage from my perspective is that we

1194
01:11:33.930 --> 01:11:37.850
