1195
01:11:37.990 --> 01:11:41.610
basal metabolic rate just needs weight, height, age, and

1196
01:11:41.730 --> 01:11:45.590
sex of the individual, and these are things that get measured pretty

1197
01:11:45.610 --> 01:11:49.430
much at every doctor's visit. And so can be easily

1198
01:11:49.510 --> 01:11:51.130
