1690
01:40:03.314 --> 01:40:06.934
So here, this is the results comparing the Confluence

1691
01:40:07.234 --> 01:40:11.054
544 variant PRS with the 313 variant PRS within

1692
01:40:11.094 --> 01:40:14.774
UK Biobank, European ancestry. We see a significant improvement

1693
01:40:15.074 --> 01:40:18.274
for 2% of AUC. So our engineered 313 PRS is roughly

1694
01:40:18.614 --> 01:40:22.564
63%, and the Confluence PRS is around 65% with significant

1695
01:40:22.614 --> 01:40:23.123
performance.

1696
01:40:24.034 --> 01:40:27.694
And we take this PRS also evaluated in the other very

1697
01:40:27.734 --> 01:40:31.114
ancestry diverse, All of Us cohort with three major ancestry,

1698
01:40:31.463 --> 01:40:34.074
European, African, and mixed American.

1699
01:40:34.094 --> 01:40:37.474
And we see consistent improvement with 2% to 3% AUC

1700
01:40:37.514 --> 01:40:40.974
improvement and all significant across all three major

1701
01:40:41.014 --> 01:40:44.243
ancestries, which is indicating this PRS show very robust

1702
01:40:44.354 --> 01:40:48.214
